                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9414" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1414</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1247 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">构建研发创新体系，助力可持续发展——N公司攀“研”逐“新”之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Building a Research and Development Innovation System to Assist Sustainable Development - N Company Climbs the Path of “Research” and Pursues “New”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡建雄，吴艺文，葛佳慧，马浩宇，张一恒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南瑞集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发创新战略；研发创新体系；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Research and Development Innovation Strategy; Research and Development Innovation System; Sustainable Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">N公司作为能源电力智能化领域的国有企业翘楚，长期引领着行业的发展潮流。在能源革命与数字革命交织前行的浪潮中，伴随着“碳达峰、碳中和”目标的明确引领，能源电力行业正经历着前所未有的深刻变革。N公司正站在一个崭新的历史起点上，既面临前所未有的机遇，也遭遇多重风险的挑战。为此，N公司从战略制定、研发创新体系构建和能源绿色转型三个关键领域入手，全面提升自身的竞争力和适应能力。本案例以N公司的转型之路为主线，聚焦N公司的转型之路，情景再现了N公司高层对企业研发创新体系的建设进行讨论，引导学员思考转型的来龙去脉、实施路径和成效。同时，N公司在研发创新绩效评估方面的宝贵经验，也为其他能源电力企业提供了借鉴的范例。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leader of state-owned enterprises in the field of energy and power intelligence, N company has long led the development trend of the industry. In the wave of energy revolution and digital revolution interwoven forward, with the clear guidance of the goal of “carbon peak, carbon neutral”, the energy and power industry is experiencing unprecedented profound changes. N Company is standing at a new historical starting point, facing both unprecedented opportunities and challenges of multiple risks. To this end, N Company starts from the three key areas of strategy formulation, R &amp; D innovation system construction and energy green transformation, and comprehensively improves its competitiveness and adaptability. This case takes the transformation path of Company N as the main line, focuses on the transformation path of Company N, reproduces the discussion of digital transformation of company N by its senior management, and guides students to think about the context, implementation path and effectiveness of the transformation. Meanwhile, N company’s valuable experience in R&amp;D innovation performance evaluation also provides a reference example for other energy and power enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理；价值创造；业务融合；绿色创新；可持续发展；平衡计分卡；关键绩效指标</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
